data.description: Rarely available, stunning corner/end unit townhome that backs up to a park like setting in Editor's Park. This 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath Clarendon model is loaded with beautiful features on every floor. This home is trendy, drenched in natural light, has an urban location steps to the metro, energy-efficient, and turn key. This townhome features hardwood floors & carpet throughout, Ryan Homes BuiltSmart energy-efficient home, zoned HVAC, rooftop terrace, and so much more! The main level features a gourmet kitchen with an island, granite countertops, custom cabinetry, GE stainless steel appliances, and a surround sound built in speaker system. The dining room/kitchen opens to a large composite deck perfect for grilling as well as a family room perfect for entertaining! The upper level features a sun-filled primary suite with an attached spa-like master bath, & walk-in closet. The second bedroom also has its very own full bath. The top-level loft offers a stunning bedroom suite with a full bath and a 2nd living room that opens to a rooftop deck with breathtaking park-like views. The ground level features a rear entry, 2 car tandem garage with storage.  At Editors Park, you are just minutes from all the major commuter routes and Prince George's Plaza Metro Station. Shop right across the street at Target, Giant Food Store, Old Navy, and the many stores at the Mall at Prince George's. This home is perfect for those who commute with the green/yellow line, well within walking distance. Book your viewing today...this one is a must see!!
